paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT drive.vehicle_id,
    drive.trip_id,
    drive.datetime,
    drive.eng_load,
    drive.rpm,
    vehicle.make,
    vehicle.max_torque,
    vehicle.max_horsepower,
    vehicle.max_horsepower_rpm,
    (drive.eng_load / 255 * vehicle.max_torque * drive.rpm / 5252) AS active_horsepower,
    (drive.eng_load / 255 * vehicle.max_torque * drive.rpm / 5252 / vehicle.max_horsepower) AS horsepower_utilization,
    (drive.eng_load / 255) AS torque_utilization,
    (drive.rpm / vehicle.max_horsepower_rpm) AS rpm_utilization
FROM drive
INNER JOIN vehicle
ON drive.vehicle_id = vehicle.vehicle_id
WHERE drive.vehicle_id = 1000500
AND drive.trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
